Name: rtp+ecn
Description:
Indicates that ICE agent has the capability to perform ECN path testing 
        for RTP-over-UDP flows.

Name: ice2
Description:
The ICE option indicates that the ICE agent using the ICE option
        is implemented according to [RFC8445].

Name: trickle
Description:
An ICE option of "trickle" indicates support for
        incremental communication of ICE candidates.
